<br>
With Cazic Thule, you need to be lucky enough to 1) get on a fear raid,  2) have Cazic Thule up,  3) have the skin drop, 4) win the roll on the skin<br>
<br>
Same goes with Venril Sathir, except you need to roll against at least 8 wizards or so every time if the staff drops(rare).<br>
<br>
The other two are possible but not easy. Both items are rare drops, but the spawn is faster.<br>
<br>
